{
  "abstract": "Your excellencies, distinguished soil scientists, delegates, ladies and\r\ngentlemen. I have great pleasure in welcoming you to the 12th International\r\nCongress of Soil Science. At the outset I must say how grateful we are to the\r\nGovernment of India, Department of Agricultural Research and Education,\r\nthe Indian Council of Agricultural Research and the Indian Society of Soil\r\nScience for inviting us to hold the 13th International Congress of Soil Science\r\nin this historic city of New Delhi and to the President of India for\r\ninaugurating it. Those of you who attended the 11 th Congress in Edmonton,\r\nCanada, will recall that the date and venue of this Congress were announced\r\nat that time.",
